<h2><a class="listing" style="document" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/Jatropha-wonder-crop-Experience-from-Swaziland" title="Jatropha - wonder crop?&quot; Experience from Swaziland" alt="document">Jatropha - wonder crop?&quot; Experience from Swaziland</a></h2>

	
	
	
	
					<p>The search for alternatives to fossil fuel has seen a rush towards biofuels. This is contributing to rising food prices and increasing concern about our ability to grow enough food and fuel. Despite social and environmental concerns and unproven climate benefits of biofuels, the EU has set a target of 10% of transport fuel to come from biofuels by 2020.</p>
