						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/Competence-and-Capacity-for-Agricultural-Development-in-Malawi" title="Competence and Capacity for Agricultural Development in Malawi" alt="link">Competence and Capacity for Agricultural Development in Malawi</a></h2>

	
					<p> <i>R. Kaarhus, Noragric Report No. 22, Agricultural University of Norway, August 2004</i>. This report gives an overview of institutions involved in knowledge generation, training and extension in agriculture and natural resource management in Malawi. It looks at how science-based competence and capacity are organised and how human resources are trained and utilised. It suggests that there are clear potentials to utilise human resources in more productive ways, and to improve institutional linkages between training, research and extension services.</p>
							<p><span class="date">22/12/2004</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/Competence-and-Capacity-for-Agricultural-Development-in-Malawi">Read more...</a>
