<h2><a class="listing" style="document" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/ACCID-News-Digest-Week-ending-15-May-2009" title="ACCID News Digest - Week ending 15 May 2009" alt="document">ACCID News Digest - Week ending 15 May 2009</a></h2>

	
	
	
	
					<p>Africa-wide Civil Society Climate Change Initiative for Policy Dialogues (ACCID) News Digest - Week ending 15 May 2009</p>
							<p><span class="date">22/05/2009</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="document" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/ACCID-News-Digest-Week-ending-15-May-2009">Read more...</a>
